    <node id="Tobias Whiting's bitterness and defeat were likely caused by the loss of his fortune and business with the Kumajis, as well as the impending attack on the colony by the Kumaji. His perception of Steve Cantwell's return was not positive, as he saw it as Steve coming to &quot;crow at their wake&quot; and rubbed in the fact that Steve left the colony to get an education while Tobias had to stay and lose everything. This is shown when he says &quot;I remember you... Had to go off to Earth to get yourself educated. What are you doing here now on that fancy aircraft of yours?&quot;" />
