    <node id="Steve Cantwell is a man who has returned to the colony where he grew up, after having left several years ago to get an education on Earth. During his visit, he learns of the passing of his aunt, who was one of the colonists affected by the poisoned water supply. Steve's history with Mary Whiting dates back ten years when she was just a young girl. At the time of their reunion, Mary is now a grown woman and shows genuine concern for Steve following the news of his aunt's passing. The depth of their relationship is not explicitly stated in the text, but it is clear that they share a history together and care for each other as old friends or acquaintances." />
